{"tid":2493501,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[推到上熱門] 今晚8點屋企要人","createTime":"2021-04-18T03:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T08:26:02.000Z","uid":281883,"like":415,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"d74dce580b58b8f340b41ca57e28ea0ef732b44f","tid":2493501,"uid":281883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:19:20.000Z","msg":"今晚就係viutv 開台以嚟第一次搞嘅音樂頒獎禮<br />\n大家成日講嘅樂壇已死 <br />\n其實除咗歌手、音樂人有責任去搞返起個樂壇<br />\n樂迷都係重要嘅一門<br />\n冇咗樂迷嘅support 佢哋出幾好聽嘅歌都冇用<br />\n<br />\n今晚18/4 20:00 99台ViuTV <br />\n《CHILL CLUB年度推介榜20/21》<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQVuwTTocnHLSNXfqMPUqh3bmrnGeTxxWyGdZTwBbhg6K?filename=tBCG7nh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtBCG7nh.png&h=a33fb56d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外 年度之歌嘅投票亦都會喺頒獎禮期間(21:00-22:00)<br />\n喺 Chill Club 官網 (<a href=\"https://chillclub.viu.tv/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchillclub.viu.tv%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RPtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=95fa1845\" target=\"_blank\">https://chillclub.viu.tv/</a>)舉行<br />\n到時候大家會以一人一票選出今屆嘅年度之歌<br />\n<br />\n除咗支持樂壇 其實仲有另一個原因<br />\n呢一個頒獎禮嘅參與人數（收看人數,投票人數）<br />\n係直接反映出ViuTV喺香港嘅討論熱度<br />\n係一個好機會令大眾信服viutv係比tvb更熱門<br />\n今次亦係ViuTV 更進一步嘅轉捩點<br />\n如果大家唔想再俾tvb做大台 <br />\n就真係要多啲宣傳吓<br />\n講同身邊嘅親戚朋友講吓<br />\n總之我要見到聽晚好多人！<br />\n今晚20:00 喺99台約定你！"},{"pid":"6b439cafa13f4d668fd8206ed0407a05df29b1c5","tid":2493501,"uid":281883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"推爆！"},{"pid":"b31f4f0d9775e6fe4eabf3f453e1e7363cf77e50","tid":2493501,"uid":281883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:19:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc1e8d857c2e35ea4ed6ccaffca8a53c3b602214","tid":2493501,"uid":281883,"like":0,"dislike":0